analysis.description: EthCashonline.payout (/unique_chucks/22/0xddaabbeb621fb90c8b10432783f228ff7f888b5f.sol#188-217) allows anyone to destruct the contract
EthCashonline.payoutSelf (/unique_chucks/22/0xddaabbeb621fb90c8b10432783f228ff7f888b5f.sol#217-240) allows anyone to destruct the contract
EthCashonline.bytesToAddress (/unique_chucks/22/0xddaabbeb621fb90c8b10432783f228ff7f888b5f.sol#241-244) is declared view but contains assembly code

EthCashonline.fallback (/unique_chucks/22/0xddaabbeb621fb90c8b10432783f228ff7f888b5f.sol#143-188) uses a dangerous strict equality:
	- user.deposits == 1

EthCashonline.payout has external calls inside a loop:
